name: Andrew Dawes
description: Andrew guides us with the wisdom of a thousand Google searches and the patience of a laptop during a software update.
bio: Andrew Dawes is a software engineer with a passion for creating beautiful, user-friendly web applications. He has a background in education and a love for teaching and learning. Andrew is a full-stack developer with experience in Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, React, and Redux. He is a graduate of the Flatiron School's software engineering program and holds a Bachelor of Arts in English from the University of Georgia. Andrew is a lifelong learner who is always looking for new ways to grow and improve his skills.
